              },
              {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Automation: Curtains — Renter Window Glow-Up\nHook: most people hang curtains too low and too narrow — here's the fix\nTone: Practical & Aspirational\nStyle: First slide is one strong scroll-stopping hook. Body slides each deliver ONE concrete, renter-safe curtain fix as an instant room transformation. Keep text short, confident, and native to TikTok slideshow memes — before/after energy, no jargon.\nMetadata requirements:\n- title: write an AI-generated title for the slideshow, 3-8 words, specific to the hook/topic.\n- caption: write a short TikTok/Instagram-style post caption for the slideshow, one sentence, specific to the hook/topic, no hashtags.\n- hashtags: give me 3-5 broad hashtags related to the topic/niche of the content, all lowercase, nothing else other than 3-5 hashtags.\nPrompt instructions:\nGenerate a concise slideshow title, a short social caption, and broad niche hashtags. Fill every non-hook placeholder text box. Use the fixed hook as context only and do not rewrite it. Body slides should be specific to the automation, not generic. Return slide text only in the schema's text object.\nStrict output rules:\n- Fill EVERY field. Never return an empty string for title, caption, hashtags, or any placeholder.\n- Keep each placeholder within the exact word range stated for it; count words before answering.\n- hashtags must be 3-5 tags, each starting with '#', separated by single spaces (e.g. '#focus #wellness #mindset').\nPlaceholders:\n- content-2__text-0jmkltys: content-2, content, Each body slide gives one concrete curtain upgrade a renter can do with no tools: hang the rod high and wide, pick the right opacity, use no-drill tension/adhesive hardware, layer sheer + blackout, correct harsh noon glare. Frame every tip as an instant, damage-free room glow-up. 5-10 words\n- content-3__text-0jmkltys: content-3, content, Each body slide gives one concrete curtain upgrade a renter can do with no tools: hang the rod high and wide, pick the right opacity, use no-drill tension/adhesive hardware, layer sheer + blackout, correct harsh noon glare. Frame every tip as an instant, damage-free room glow-up. 5-10 words\n- content-4__text-0jmkltys: content-4, content, Each body slide gives one concrete curtain upgrade a renter can do with no tools: hang the rod high and wide, pick the right opacity, use no-drill tension/adhesive hardware, layer sheer + blackout, correct harsh noon glare. Frame every tip as an instant, damage-free room glow-up. 5-10 words\n- content-5__text-0jmkltys: content-5, content, Each body slide gives one concrete curtain upgrade a renter can do with no tools: hang the rod high and wide, pick the right opacity, use no-drill tension/adhesive hardware, layer sheer + blackout, correct harsh noon glare. Frame every tip as an instant, damage-free room glow-up. 5-10 words\n- cta-6__text-xojfy3qf: cta-6, cta, comment RENT and i'll send the no-drill curtain list — save this before you buy curtains. 5-10 words"
              }
